caption.p: Viscosity and rheological behavior of the tested honeys. MH1: manuka honey containing methylglyoxal 400 + mg/kg, ARJ: arjuna honey, GUG: guggul honey, JIA: jiaogulan honey and OLI: olive honey. The viscosity of all the tested honeys remained constant with the increase in experimental shear rate, indicating their Newtonian liquid behavior.
